| `is_core_team()` | common.sh:280 | Window matches core team window |
| `is_task_reviewer()` | common.sh:286 | Core team, pane 1 |
| `is_deployment()` | common.sh:290 | Core team, pane 2 |
| `is_doey_expert()` | common.sh:294 | Core team, pane 3 |

**No `is_planner()` or similar function exists.**

